1)
As an air traffic controller
So I can get passengers to a destination
I want to instruct a plane to land at an airport and confirm that it has landed

Nouns: air traffic controller, passengers, plane, airport
Verbs: instruct to land, confirm landed

Object            Messages
-------------------------------------
controller       instruct, confirm
passengers
plane              land
airport

controller=>instruct=>plane<=land<=airport
controller=>confirm landed<=plane




2) As an air traffic controller
So I can get passengers on the way to their destination
I want to instruct a plane to take off from an airport and confirm that it is no longer in the airport

Nouns: air traffic controller, passengers, destination, plane, airport
Verbs: instruct, take off, confirm take off

Object            Messages
------------------------------------
controller        instruct, confirm
passengers
plane              take off
airport

controller=>instruct=>plane<=takeoff<=airport
controller=>confirm takeoff<=plane
